  in very good way i had very good experince here i was staying in capital city of
  nicosia meet many local guys and women they are friendly nature and very polite
  and ready to help you in every way they can the people here speak greek and english
  and it has other cities like larnaca and aiya napa which have many beaches very
  beautiful atmospher and cost of living is very low here i love food you have different
  varities of food because of mix culture with turkey greece it was very wonderful
  trip to cyprus
